\lang english
They are going to drive you crazy.
 Your phone operator, your bank, your daughter's school, your dog's veterinarian
, even your ISP; it seems like all of them are trying to drown you under
 tons of papers.
 Papers you have to read, classify, and memorize just in case you may need
 them later.
 Most of the time you won't, which means you waste your energy for nothing.
\end_layout

